author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Kuwait's Livestock Transport and Trading FY Profit Falls

organizations.name: livestock transport and trading fy profit falls feb

text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - LIVESTOCK TRANSPORT AND TRADING CO KPSC :
* FY NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO SHAREHOLDERS 2.6 ‍​MILLION DINARS VERSUS 3.9 ‍​MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* FY TOTAL OPERATING REVENUE 64.7 ‍​MILLION DINARS VERSUS 56.1 ‍​MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* BOARD PROPOSES CASH DIVIDEND OF 5 FILS PER SHARE FOR YEAR 2017 Source: ( bit.ly/2BKcWoZ ) Further company coverage:
